{"time": "00:50:10.737", "event": "llm_output", "round": 7, "content": "### Compute a 30‑day rolling correlation between the Bitcoin and S&P 500 return series and store it as `RollingCorr30d` in **btc_spx_ma**\n\n```r\nbtc_spx_ma <- btc_spx_ma %>%\n  mutate(\n    RollingCorr30d = {\n      btc_ret <- Bitcoin_30d_ret\n      spx_ret <- SPX_30d_ret\n      sapply(seq_along(btc_ret), function(i) {\n        if (i < 30) {\n          NA_real_\n        } else {\n          cor(btc_ret[(i - 29):i], spx_ret[(i - 29):i], use = \"complete.obs\")\n        }\n      })\n    }\n  )\n```", "empty": false}
