{"time": "00:24:20.080", "event": "llm_output", "round": 9, "content": "**Cleaning up the dataset** – we’ll keep only the columns that are useful for further analysis (the original Bitcoin data, the 30‑day MA, the SPX return, the up‑trend signal, the portfolio daily return, and the cumulative portfolio value) and drop the intermediate SPX price/volume columns.\n\n```r\n# Keep only the necessary columns\nbitcoin_daily_5y <- bitcoin_daily_5y %>%\n  select(\n    Date,\n    Open, High, Low, Close, Volume_USD,\n    Circulating_Supply_Est, Market_Cap_Est,\n    MA30,\n    spx_Return", "empty": false}
