{"time": "20:43:18.129", "event": "llm_output", "round": 5, "content": "**Step 6 – Calculate cumulative total returns**  \nWe’ll create two new columns:\n\n* `Cum_Strategy` – cumulative return of the trend‑following strategy (`Strategy_Return`).\n* `Cum_BuyHold` – cumulative return of a simple buy‑and‑hold (just the daily price return).\n\n`coalesce(..., 0)` replaces the initial `NA` (first day) with 0 so that `cumprod()` starts from a neutral 1.\n\n```r\nbitcoin_daily_5y <- bitcoin_daily_5y %>%\n  mutate(\n    Cum_Strategy = cumprod(1 + coalesce(Strategy_Return, 0)) - 1,\n    ", "empty": false}
