{"time": "20:43:13.521", "event": "llm_output", "round": 4, "content": "**Step 5 – Compute the strategy’s daily returns**  \nWe multiply the lagged trend‑following signal (`Signal_lag`) by the daily price return (`Daily_Return`). The result is stored in a new column `Strategy_Return`.\n\n```r\n# Compute the strategy’s daily returns\nbitcoin_daily_5y <- bitcoin_daily_5y %>%\n  mutate(\n    # (Re‑creates Daily_Return if it already exists – values stay the same)\n    Daily_Return   = (Close / lag(Close)) - 1,\n    Strategy_Return = Signal_lag * Daily_Return\n  )\n```", "empty": false}
